# Live current-market pricing (optional but recommended for current-year vehicles)
#
# Without a key, the app falls back to the ML model (trained on 2014-2015 data)
# and shows a "Model estimate" badge + an out-of-coverage warning for recent years.
#
# To enable CURRENT market prices:
#   1. Sign up (free) at https://www.marketcheck.com/apis  (free tier ~500 calls/month)
#   2. Copy your API key below
#   3. Start the API with this variable set, e.g.:
#        MARKETCHECK_API_KEY=your_key_here PYTHONPATH=. python3 -m uvicorn idss.api.main:app --port 8000
#
# Alternative provider (Auto.dev, 1000 free calls/month) can be swapped in
# src/idss/data/live_pricing.py.

MARKETCHECK_API_KEY=
# MARKETCHECK_BASE_URL=https://mc-api.marketcheck.com/v2
